</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:402px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Kevin-Trudeau-Dianetics.png" class="image" title="Trudeau endorses Dianetics on page 226 of The Weight Loss Cure &quot;They&quot; Don't Want You to Know About under the heading &quot;Things STRONGLY SUGGESTED you do&quot; (emphasis in original)"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/82/Kevin-Trudeau-Dianetics.png/400px-Kevin-Trudeau-Dianetics.png" width="400" height="163" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
