Trudeau endorses <a href="/wiki/Dianetics" title="Dianetics">Dianetics</a> on page 226 of <i>The Weight Loss Cure "They" Don't Want You to Know About</i> under the heading "Things STRONGLY SUGGESTED you do" <i>(emphasis in original)</i></div>
</div>
